<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Emmanuel</title>
<aka>Immanuel</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Immanuel, Immanuel,
 Hans navn er kalt Immanuel.
 Gud med oss, Gud vår styrke er,
 Ditt navn er Gud, Immanuel.

[V2]
 Emmanuel, Emmanuel;
 His name is called Emmanuel.
 He's God with us,
 Revealed in us,
 His name is called Emmanuel.</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>